description:
Ellen White wasn't the only one to receive visions from God. Two men, William Foy and Hazen Foss also received the prophecy gift during the 1840s, though each would have vastly different experiences in their life and ministry. One was faithful and shared what he had seen, and was one unfaithful to the call with very sobering consequences.

To find out more information about Hazen Foss & William Foy read our extended article on our website.
